%%{init: {'theme': 'base', 'themeVariables': { 'fontFamily': 'Microsoft YaHei' }}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 用户
    participant F as 前端工作台
    participant A as /api/sessions + /messages
    participant S as SessionStore
    participant C as AssistantChatService
    participant M as SessionMemoryEngine / Mem0
    participant K as Teaching 检索
    participant L as LLM

    U->>F: 登录后直接输入问题
    F->>A: POST /api/sessions {scene_key: chat, query}
    A->>S: create session + 写入 user message
    A->>C: reply(state, query)
    C->>M: hydrate_state / search memory
    C->>K: search(query, limit=4)
    C->>L: 生成自然语言回复
    L-->>C: assistant text + suggested scene keys
    C-->>A: message response
    A->>S: update context + 写入 assistant message
    A-->>F: {type: message, text, suggested_scene_keys}
    F-->>U: 展示聊天结果与模块建议

    U->>F: 继续追问
    F->>A: POST /api/sessions/{id}/messages
    A->>S: 追加 user message
    A->>C: reply(state, follow-up)
    C->>M: 读取账户记忆
    C->>K: 补充知识片段
    C->>L: 结合历史对话生成回复
    A->>S: 更新会话上下文
    A-->>F: 多轮聊天结果
